tags.name: 31.1.1/rev1312/amd64
tags.body:
feat!: migrate to core24 and rebase on official PPA (#220)

  • base the snap on core24, build from official PPA

  • use obs-wrapper for launching the snap

  • Add a script for getting the latest PPA deb url and version

  • move the –multi comment in the wrapper where the option is

  • replaced majority of the bind-mounts with patching the binaries with a different rpath

  • sort dependencies

  • add a comment to explain the need for patchelf

  • remove unused paths from env variables

  • integrate the script for ppa version into GH action

  • add alsa library

  • README: move camera info and add sound info

  • update to 31.1.0, use PPA with package-repositories, add the ffmpeg plug

  • add hardware encoding support (Intel QSV)

  • remove redundant dependencies

  • add LIBVA_DRIVERS_PATH

  • update to 31.1.1
